<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/biphenyl> skos:definition "Biphenyl ((C6H5)2), a polycyclic aromatic hydrocarbon (PAH), also known as diphenyl or phenylbenzene or 1,1'-biphenyl or lemonene" ;
