<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/effectiveEnergyAndMassTransfer> skos:definition "Effective energy and mass transfer (EEMT) couples energy and mass flux to the subsurface in the form of effective precipitation and net primary production in a common energy unit." ;
