<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/heatIndex> skos:definition "The combination effect of heat and humidity on the temperature felt by people." ;
    skos:historyNote "Originally from the CUAHSI HIS VariableNameCV.  See: http://his.cuahsi.org/mastercvreg/edit_cv11.aspx?tbl=VariableNameCV." ;
