<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/hydrogen_2_StableIsotopeRatioDelta> skos:definition "Difference in the 2H:1H ratio between the sample and standard" ;
    skos:historyNote "Originally from the CUAHSI HIS VariableNameCV.  See: http://his.cuahsi.org/mastercvreg/edit_cv11.aspx?tbl=VariableNameCV." ;
