<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/mica> skos:definition "The mica group of sheet silicate minerals includes several closely related materials having nearly perfect basal cleavage. All are monoclinic, with a tendency towards pseudohexagonal crystals, and are similar in chemical composition." ;
