    skos:topConceptOf <http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename> .

<http://vocabulary.odm2.org/variablename/microsomalProtein> skos:definition "The total protein concentration within the microsomal fraction of cells. Microsomes refer to vesicle-like artifacts reformed from pieces of endoplasmic reticulum when eukaryotic cells are broken up in a laboratory." ;
