    skos:note "This group includes parameters describing the transfer of water to the atmosphere through evapotranspiration, which combines evaporation from land and water surfaces with plant transpiration. It includes evapotranspiration rates, totals, and potential evapotranspiration. This group does not originally exist in RISE and contains parameters from usgs-sta."@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "Evapotranspiration"@en ;
    skos:topConceptOf <http://lincolninst.edu/cgs/vocabularies/usbr#conceptScheme_8257cf0e> .

<http://lincolninst.edu/cgs/vocabularies/usbr#c_e3222c25> skos:broader <http://lincolninst.edu/cgs/vocabularies/usbr#c_c1f57079> ;
